flowchart TB
    subgraph Client[Trusted client boundary]
        CLI[Wenvy CLI<br/>K-V working state and index<br/>merge, sign, encrypt, decrypt]
        Agent[Memory-only key agent<br/>master/recovery unlock]
        Local[Encrypted .wenvy state<br/>objects, refs, index, stash]
        CLI <--> Agent
        CLI <--> Local
    end

    subgraph Identity[External identity and automation]
        Email[Email provider]
        GitHub[GitHub App<br/>read-only membership]
        CICD[CI/CD service account<br/>token + signed requests]
    end

    subgraph Edge[Cloudflare edge]
        Web[Dashboard and API Worker<br/>governance only]
        Tunnel[Cloudflare Tunnel or Spectrum]
        SSH[Go SSH gateway<br/>typed fetch/push protocol]
        DO[Durable Objects<br/>tokens, refs, rotation leases]
        Queues[Queues and Cron<br/>email, sync, checks]
        WF[Workflows<br/>wait for client rotation artifacts]
        Web --> DO
        Web --> Queues
        Web --> WF
        Tunnel --> SSH
        SSH --> DO
    end

    subgraph Transparency[Key transparency]
        Log[Append-only Merkle directory]
        W1[Witness 1]
        W2[Witness 2]
        W3[Witness 3]
        Log --> W1
        Log --> W2
        Log --> W3
    end

    subgraph State[Untrusted for secret plaintext]
        Hyperdrive[Hyperdrive]
        PG[(Postgres<br/>identity, RBAC, envelopes,<br/>commits, refs, audit, jobs)]
        R2[(R2<br/>encrypted bundles and<br/>item payloads only)]
        Hyperdrive --> PG
    end

    CLI -->|SSH| Tunnel
    CLI -->|HTTPS governance and proofs| Web
    CICD -->|HTTPS| Web
    Web --> Hyperdrive
    Web --> R2
    SSH --> Hyperdrive
    SSH --> R2
    Queues --> Hyperdrive
    WF --> Hyperdrive
    WF -.->|rotation claim/event| CLI
    Web --> Log
    CLI -->|inclusion + consistency proofs| Log
    Email --> Web
    GitHub -->|signed webhooks| Web
    Queues -->|reconcile| GitHub

    subgraph Keys[Envelope hierarchy]
        UK[User X25519 key]
        GK[Group Key]
        VK[Branch Vault Key]
        DEK[Item-version DEK]
        Payload[Encrypted key + value]
        UK --> GK --> VK --> DEK --> Payload
    end

    CLI -.->|creates and unwraps| Keys
    R2 -.->|stores ciphertext| Payload
    PG -.->|stores envelopes| GK
    PG -.->|stores envelopes| VK
    PG -.->|stores envelopes| DEK

    subgraph RefFlow[Branch update]
        A[Authenticate SSH key]
        B[Authorize group and branch policy]
        C[Require active crypto state]
        D[Validate signed immutable objects]
        E[Compare expected old head]
        F[Move ref and audit transactionally]
        A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F
    end

    SSH -.-> RefFlow
